to compile

c++ -Wall -I `root-config --cflags` -o plot  main.cc   Event.cc BraggStatistic.cc EventDump.cc EventReadFromFile.cc EventSource.cc EnergyDist.cc  AnalysisSteering.cc  SourceFactory.cc AnalysisInfo.cc EventSim.cc  `root-config --libs`


to run

./plot input FILE.txt

./plot input sim n m 
(simulate n events with random seed m)
